  | IBM Concert   (concert - 11 kinds)
    concert_application                 software         A Concert application
                                                         is the top-level
                                                         managed entity in IBM
                                                         Concert's inventory —
                                                         the unit Concert tracks
                                                         for risk posture,
                                                         vulnerabilities,
                                                         dependencies, and
                                                         resilience.
